Frequently Asked Questions Rewards, competitions, and how Step Karma works
How do I earn rewards and tokens?
Your daily steps are tracked and converted into progress toward milestones. As you hit goals, you earn tokens that can be used to unlock rewards and enter competitions (for example, 10,000 steps = 1 token, where applicable).
What types of challenges and competitions are available?
Step Karma offers daily challenges, weekly leaderboards, and special limited-time events. Join, stay consistent, and climb the rankings to unlock bonus rewards and additional entries.
What rewards can I unlock or win?
Rewards may include partner discounts, vouchers, exclusive offers, and prize drops during major competitions. Reward availability can vary based on your region, activity level, and current partner campaigns.
How are rankings and winners determined?
Rankings are calculated from verified step totals during the competition window. Winners are selected automatically based on the rules of each event (leaderboard placement or lucky draw entries), ensuring a fair and transparent outcome.
How do Brand Partners contribute to rewards?
Brand Partners sponsor rewards, offers, and competition prizes. If youâ€™d like to become a partner, select a sponsor package and contact the Step Karma team to get featured and launch a campaign.
